description: Redevelopment to provide 798 residential units (including 40.2% affordable housing) 959 sq m Class A1/A2/A3/A4/A5/D1 & D2 floorpsace; 7927 sq m of Class B1(a),(b),(c) floorspace including a business incubator centre; creation of a new access onto Whitchurch Lane; associated flood alleviation, landscaping, car parking and highway works.
